ystery before it's too late!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824040/extras/13ff57bbea3df1a49e1b99b55d8d4ae3.poster.avif?t=1770760633\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824040/extras/13ff57bbea3df1a49e1b99b55d8d4ae3.webm?t=1770760633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824040/extras/13ff57bbea3df1a49e1b99b55d8d4ae3.mp4?t=1770760633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824040/extras/6ed66f0d3c91db88cdb26db5ef285bbb.webp?t=1770760633\" width=525 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A soundtrack from multiple independent artists that enhances the experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824040/extras/f2413236568931aa7df8e64ca705e5b3.poster.avif?t=1770760633\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824040/extras/f2413236568931aa7df8e64ca705e5b3.webm?t=1770760633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824040/extras/f2413236568931aa7df8e64ca705e5b3.mp4?t=1770760633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
